tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">▲天下武功唯快不破，打到我算你输！</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://p9.pstatp.com/large/46ec000366b5f19e63e5\" alt=\"就凭你的破外挂也想吃到鸡？别做梦了！\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; display: block; margin: 10px auto;\"/></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">▲铁掌水上漂，不用吊威亚的那种！</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/46f0000186f82209b4e0\" alt=\"就凭你的破外挂也想吃到鸡？别做梦了！\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; display: block; margin: 10px auto;\"/></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">▲阳顶天在此，尔等休要放肆！</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/46ef0003050d87658b75\" alt=\"就凭你的破外挂也想吃到鸡？别做梦了！\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; display: block; margin: 10px auto;\"/></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">▲听说枪越大越厉害？那我的枪在吧里什么水平？</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">就问你服不服？终于知道这游戏外挂为什么收费那么贵了，因为贫穷会限制外挂制作者的想象力呀！！！妈耶这些挂凑到一起PK堪比武侠小说华山论剑了，什么自动瞄准的挂，遇见这些BT挂根本没有卵用好吗？然而后边还有，坐稳了！</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-weight: 700;\">挂逼A：唉，这游戏全是挂！我在天上看的一清二楚！</span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-weight: 700;\">挂逼B：无需多言，放眼望去只有阁下才能称得上是个对手，出招吧！</span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/46ed000349c775f98790\" alt=\"就凭你的破外挂也想吃到鸡？别做梦了！\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; display: block; margin: 10px auto;\"/></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">▲这才是真正的决赛圈！决战世界之巅</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/46f10000e59152c33e36\" alt=\"就凭你的破外挂也想吃到鸡？别做梦了！\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; display: block; margin: 10px auto;\"/></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">▲楼上的都装什么B？让你们都下不了飞机信不信？</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://p9.pstatp.com/large/46f0000186fb7e567812\" alt=\"就凭你的破外挂也想吃到鸡？别做梦了！\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; display: block; margin: 10px auto;\"/></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">▲说别人装逼的人你别装逼知道吗，我让你上不了飞机你信不信？</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">哈哈哈哈哈，我只想说开发绝地求生外挂的人各个都是人才，外挂又实用功能还搞笑，简直没谁了！<span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-weight: 700;\">想吃到鸡？也不撒泡尿照照自己的破外挂够不够资格！</span>照这么发展下去，估计将来就会开发出来烧你网线炸你电脑拉你家小区电闸门的挂了！好可怕，还是和粉丝玩一波农药压压惊吧。明天见！！！</p>', null);
INSERT INTO `art_content` VALUES ('53196236', '<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">文|AI财经社周晶晶</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">编|鹿鸣</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">“月零花钱600万、每年发微信红包300万、2天入手两套千万级豪宅”，12月2日，“微商专家”龚文祥在微博发出该条信息后，立即引发网友热议。一时间，“吹牛、炫富、造假”成为质疑的焦点。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/4ae4000054de87e0a363\" alt=\"微商教父自称每月零花钱600万，两天买深圳两套豪宅，你信吗？\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; display: block; margin: 10px auto;\"/></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">4小时后，他在微博表达了自己的态度——“今天骂我的人很多，目的达到了”、“不撕逼不会火”、“这一个事件，就会让我一个（微信）号加满5000人”。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">公开信息显示，龚文祥名下的深圳触电信息技术有限责任公司成立于2016年，注册资本10万元，实缴金额6.5万元，如此“家底”如何为龚文祥带来日购千万级豪宅的资金，仍是一个谜。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">12月3日，AI财经社联系上龚文祥，但他表示该条信息发出后引发不小争议，不想让触电平台正常运营受妨碍，暂时不接受采访。</p><h1 style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-size: 24px; margin-top: 36px; margin-bottom: 22px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 32px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">自称2天入手2套千万级豪宅</h1><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">打开龚文祥微信朋友圈，扑面而来的是具有极具辨识度的微商专用画风——三天两头聚会、早晚灌鸡汤、一夜暴富的财富神话，他更新朋友圈的频率也相当高，日均20条以上。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">在外界赋予龚文祥的头衔中，“第一人、一哥”等关键词时常出现——中国电商第一自媒体人、全中国最赚钱的自媒体人、全中国微信发红包最多第一人。常常开设“如何在微电商社群做到千万生意”类似成功学的直播、讲座，直播评论中，除了质疑和嘲讽的声音，不乏被财富故事打动的网友。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">他还是个红包概念熟手，触电会会员建立社群将他拉入群，他都会发红包，并将这种行为称作“红包营销”。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">“红包营销在于先付出再求回报，付出越多，越敢秀，回报越大。”12月2日，在“2018年龚文祥触电会”228人群里，一位成员在分享龚文祥的语录，“打造好自己的私人20个微信号，一年赚1000万是有可能的。”</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">在中国，挣大钱的一般都比较避讳说自己的收入，但在微商圈，晒豪车、豪宅、成捆的大红人民币，是一种常态和业务红火的标志。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">龚文祥曾表示自己“买房如买菜”、“2天入手2套千万级豪宅”、“月零花钱600万每年发微信红包300万”，但这些数据都无从考证。这也与群成员分享的“越敢秀，回报越大”相契合。在龚文祥的微博和朋友圈中，不乏这类看似激励人心的鸡汤。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/4ae10000aa409b02f258\" alt=\"微商教父自称每月零花钱600万，两天买深圳两套豪宅，你信吗？\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; display: block; margin: 10px auto;\"/></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://p1.pstatp.com/large/4ae30000a4b58648c4ba\" alt=\"微商教父自称每月零花钱600万，两天买深圳两套豪宅，你信吗？\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; display: block; margin: 10px auto;\"/></p><h1 style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-size: 24px; margin-top: 36px; margin-bottom: 22px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 32px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">“能加粉丝就能赚钱”</h1><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">“谦虚使人落后，骄傲使人进步”，龚文祥多次在微博表达了这一观点；</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">“现在是一个抛弃几千年传统智慧反而能成功的新时代”，12月2日，认证为深圳触电电子商务有限公司的@触电报微博发文表示。深圳触电信息技术有限责任公司是龚文祥旗下公司，他常常在线下组织叫做“触电会”的“私密电商俱乐部”。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">和常见的微商不同的是，龚文祥并没有销售实际的产品，许多网友也对其赚钱的方式颇感好奇。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">问题的答案可以从其朋友圈中窥视一二。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">12月3日，龚文祥发文称：一个年轻人，如果一年不追剧、不打王者荣耀，每天16小时到处加粉丝、发朋友圈，每个5000人的（微信）号都一对一聊天，维护好几万粉丝维护好，做到努力勤奋，一年赚几百万元是有结果的。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">也就是说，龚文祥所提倡的“努力勤奋”的方式，就是维护粉丝。他认为粉丝可以变现为钱。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">“我自己都佩服自己是个营销高手，昨天炫富引起关注，但虚的知名度意义不大，如何将知名度变成钱？能加粉丝以后就会变成钱。叫好不行，必须叫座，这才是真正的落地营销。”</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">在微博中，龚文祥曾自曝过自己的收入来源，其中包括，每年1000个交了2万元的触电会会员社群收入；10个每年36万元的年度客户及10个触电报年度客户；10万元每次的出场费，8000元每次私人号广告等。</p><h1 style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-size: 24px; margin-top: 36px; margin-bottom: 22px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 32px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">6.5万起家，2次被列入经营异常名单</h1><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">据国家企业信息信用公示系统信息，深圳触电信息技术有限责任公司成立于2016年，注册资本10万元，实缴金额6.5万元，龚文祥持股99%，任公司总经理、法定代表人，主营业务包括网络技术开发、网上电子数码产品销售等。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">一个号称年入5000万以上级别的“教父级”人物，其主体公司实缴资金不到十万元，实在有些匪夷所思。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://p9.pstatp.com/large/4ae10000aa410a3a5f7a\" alt=\"微商教父自称每月零花钱600万，两天买深圳两套豪宅，你信吗？\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; display: block; margin: 10px auto;\"/></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">天眼查资料显示，他担任法人的深圳市南山区品牌先生策划工作室曾因未按规定提交2013年-2015年的年度报告，三次被列入企业经营异常名单。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">2017年7月，龚文祥旗下公司深圳触电电子商务有限公司因登记的住所或经营场所无法联系、未按规定期限公示2016年度报告被列入企业经营异常名单，8月办理住所（经营场所）变更登记、公示年度报告后被移除。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">据公开资料，龚文祥毕业于武汉大学工商管理系，他在个人微博上也多次提到自己是武汉大学校友，从“珞珈山出来”。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">创业之前做过保健品推广；2007年初担任美国电子商务公司MeziMedia中国市场策划高级总监，投身电子商务热潮；2007年底，加盟主打线上奢侈品销售的走秀网并担任副总裁，负责品牌和市场推广业务，2012年，龚文祥创办触电电子商务有限公司，此后长期招募会员，打着“微商教父”的头衔，在线下举办电商人的私密聚会（触电会）。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">AI财经社注意到，龚文祥在微博上有408万粉丝，按粉丝数量来说可以跻身微博大V行列，其发微博的频率也非常频繁，平均每天15条以上，但粉丝评论通常只有个位数。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">【更多报道请移步 AI财经社微信公众号（ID:aicjnews）和官方网站 www.aicaijing.com.cn 】</p>', null);
INSERT INTO `art_content` VALUES ('53196237', '<img style=\"margin: 10px auto; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; display: block; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\" alt=\"山西一村民碾死工商局一官员宠物狗 被其家人殴打致骨折 目前警方已立案\" src=\"http://p1.pstatp.com/large/4a3c000be41b08292647\"/><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">近日，山西阳城县一村民杨三社在驾车时将一宠物狗碾死，随后其被狗主人打致肋骨骨折。打人者为山西省工商局副处长张广太的家人。北青报记者获悉，目前，阳城县公安局已立案，具体情况正在调查中。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">今天下午，北青报记者联系上杨三社的儿子杨飞飞。他告诉记者，11月23日上午，他正在镇上的单位上班，接到其母亲的电话得知父亲被打了。随后，他赶往事发地点次营镇庄头村，看到父亲坐在地上，脸上沾满血迹，口腔里也流满了血。在父亲的旁边站着十几个人。一个女子在哭喊着说她的宠物狗被碾死了。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">据54岁的伤者杨三社介绍，11月23日上午，他驾驶面包车路过次营镇庄头村，公路右边有人在聊天，所以他打方向靠左行驶，此时两个小狗在路上玩耍，一只白狗跑到他车的后轮处被轧住。他停车后被人拽下车遭到两人轮番殴打。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">杨飞飞称，当时他了解这一情况之后，就给当地派出所拨打了报警电话，并与母亲一起将父亲送到医院，“我们把父亲抬到车上，对方没有搭一把手。”</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">记者从其提供的一份阳城县瘤医院的检查报告显示，杨三社右侧第11肋骨骨折。对此，杨飞飞告诉北青报记者，从住院到现在医药费已经花了5000多块钱，均是自己支付，对方未前来探望。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">北青报记者了解到，涉事人员系山西省工商局张广太的家人。公开资料显示，山西省工商局今年4月25日曾发布任命通知，其中，任命张广太为该局商标监督管理处副处长，试用期一年。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">随后，北青报记者联系到张广太本人，他称，“我们一家人打人，这个确实有，但我确实没有动手。”</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">据张广太介绍，确实是因为宠物狗被碾死，双方才起的冲突。“被碾死的宠物狗是朋友花了一万多从国外买回来的，他不要了，给了我。我们一家人养这只宠物狗10年了，这个狗跟我们都有了感情。”</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">今天下午，北青报记者致电阳城县次营镇派出所。一名工作人员表示，目前，警方已立案，具体情况正在调查中，调查结果出来之后，会对外公布。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">（文/北青报记者马金凤）</p>', null);
INSERT INTO `art_content` VALUES ('53196238', '<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(80, 80, 80); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: helvetica; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-wrap: break-word; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">海淘</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(80, 80, 80); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: helvetica; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-wrap: break-word; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">近几年网购发展迅速,人们足不出户,就可以享受到其他国家的优质产品。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(80, 80, 80); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: helvetica; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-wrap: break-word; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">然而,某些电商网站大量的“境外购”“海外购”,真的是从国外漂洋过海买来的产品吗?</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(80, 80, 80); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: helvetica; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-wrap: break-word; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">下面这个视频,看完实在让人大吃一惊。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(80, 80, 80); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: helvetica; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-wrap: break-word; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">STEP 1:制造假货</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(80, 80, 80); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: helvetica; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-wrap: break-word; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><img style=\"background: rgb(239, 239, 239); margin: 8px auto; border-radius: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; display: block; max-width: 100%;\" alt=\"央视曝光!这些全是假货没一件真的 有些人还在买\" src=\"http://3g.youth.cn/rdzx/201712/W020171205232110171879.jpeg\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(80, 80, 80); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: helvetica; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-wrap: break-word; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">以鞋类为例。白天,工人在厂里热火朝天地生产, 夜晚,他们回家“发挥余热”,制鞋“秘方”被或偷或买地传了出来。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(80, 80, 80); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: helvetica; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-wrap: break-word; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">这些无疑都是假货,但“鬼市”里的人们都回避“假”字。他们发明了自己的话语体系,“真标”“高仿”“1︰1”,造假者则叫“阿冒”。?有人在名牌的基础上,加了几个数字或字母,并拿到了商标注册。在外边,有人称其为“山寨”,但在“鬼市”,它们有着微妙的名字——“擦边鞋”。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(80, 80, 80); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: helvetica; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-wrap: break-word; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">STEP 2:伪造发货单、查验网站</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(80, 80, 80); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: helvetica; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-wrap: break-word; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">接着,黄牛伪造国外假快递单、电子单!明明是国内城市发货的单子,被伪造成美国等地发货的快递信息!</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(80, 80, 80); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: helvetica; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-wrap: break-word; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><img style=\"background: rgb(239, 239, 239); margin: 8px auto; border-radius: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; display: block; max-width: 100%;\" alt=\"央视曝光!这些全是假货没一件真的 有些人还在买\" src=\"http://3g.youth.cn/rdzx/201712/W020171205232110252267.jpeg\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(80, 80, 80); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: helvetica; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-wrap: break-word; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">国内淘变海外淘,?假商品,假防伪,再加上假快递单助力,一条龙的制假售假链条就完成了。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(80, 80, 80); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: helvetica; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-wrap: break-word; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">用手机扫描这些发票的二维码,页面全能弹出专卖店的地址;刮开涂层,登录所谓“全国质量防伪监督中心”网站,输入验证码后真的可以查到。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(80, 80, 80); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: helvetica; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-wrap: break-word; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">事实上,这只是“鬼市”虚构出的认证世界,并引导顾客认真地走到这里——弹出页面仅是用二维码生成软件做出来的,所谓查验网站疑似“山寨”,其ICP备案信息主办单位是某私企。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(80, 80, 80); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: helvetica; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-wrap: break-word; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><img style=\"background: rgb(239, 239, 239); margin: 8px auto; border-radius: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; display: block; max-width: 100%;\" alt=\"央视曝光!这些全是假货没一件真的 有些人还在买\" src=\"http://3g.youth.cn/rdzx/201712/W020171205232110283917.jpeg\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(80, 80, 80); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: helvetica; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-wrap: break-word; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><img style=\"background: rgb(239, 239, 239); margin: 8px auto; border-radius: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; display: block; max-width: 100%;\" alt=\"央视曝光!这些全是假货没一件真的 有些人还在买\" src=\"http://3g.youth.cn/rdzx/201712/W020171205232110290703.jpeg\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(80, 80, 80); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: helvetica; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-wrap: break-word; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">多家快递企业当时都出面回应。 有快递公司表示,视频拍摄场所非快递营业网点,视频中所提及的海外网站系黄牛自建,并非快递公司内部存在协助。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(80, 80, 80); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: helvetica; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-wrap: break-word; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">具体情况如何,还待有关部门的进一步调查。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(80, 80, 80); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: helvetica; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-wrap: break-word; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">网友热评</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(80, 80, 80); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: helvetica; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-wrap: break-word; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">小文是我:不管是否跟大牌快递企业有关,加强监管都是必须的</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(80, 80, 80); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: helvetica; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-wrap: break-word; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">JasmineK:市场秩序何在?请给老百姓一个交代</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(80, 80, 80); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: helvetica; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-wrap: break-word; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">图图是6嘛:太可怕,以后都不敢买了</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(80, 80, 80); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: helvetica; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-wrap: break-word; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">嘿嘿呀呀:造假都成产业化了么。。</p>', null);
INSERT INTO `art_content` VALUES ('53196239', '<p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><img style=\"margin: 10px auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\" alt=\"矢野浩二为在节目中称中国人没资格养狗道歉，网友：你说得对！\" src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/4add0003d035f96d24dc\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">如果说秋瓷炫是在中国口碑最好的韩国艺人，那么日本明星中，最受待见的应该是抗日剧鬼子专业户矢野浩二了吧。曾是《天天向上》固定主持班底的他，由于种种原因不得退出舞台，结果只能跑回日本电视剧中演中国人。在最近热播的电视剧《海上牧云记》中，想念浩二的观众又看到了他，不过刚一露脸，又被黑了，他几年前在日本节目中所说的一段话，被断章取义拿出来说事。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><img style=\"margin: 10px auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\" alt=\"矢野浩二为在节目中称中国人没资格养狗道歉，网友：你说得对！\" src=\"http://p9.pstatp.com/large/4ada000411fed8bc6733\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><img style=\"margin: 10px auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\" alt=\"矢野浩二为在节目中称中国人没资格养狗道歉，网友：你说得对！\" src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/4adb00040c23743b6fdb\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">12月4日下午，矢野浩二在微博道歉，他说道：“没想到几年前录制的综艺节目被有心人翻出来说，在这里向大家致歉，在节目里说的个别现象经过剪辑后让大家误解为XX，我的言论有失分寸，以偏概全，以后一定注意，老婆孩子都是中国人，我是中国的女婿，中国就是我的第二故乡，说我XX，我是辱我自己吗，最后感谢支持我的中国观众和粉丝朋友，看到大家这么支持我没被这些无聊的人影响真的是太开心了，开心开心极了，我爱中国，我永远爱你们.一直爱，永远爱。”</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">究竟发生了什么事？很多网友被浩二突如其来的道歉给整懵了。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><img style=\"margin: 10px auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\" alt=\"矢野浩二为在节目中称中国人没资格养狗道歉，网友：你说得对！\" src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/4adb00040c4f4af2f0e0\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">原来，近日，有人将浩二几年前在日本节目中所说的一段话截了出来，并给他扣上看不起中国人的帽子。在节目中，矢野浩二聊到有关中国人养狗的问题，他的观点是“中国人没资格养狗”，原因是，很多中国人养狗不仅遛狗不牵绳子，主人也没有随时备好纸巾报纸清理狗大便的习惯。以至于不少公园啊小区四处可见狗大便。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><img style=\"margin: 10px auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\" alt=\"矢野浩二为在节目中称中国人没资格养狗道歉，网友：你说得对！\" src=\"http://p9.pstatp.com/large/4add0003cf3b9a463ffa\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">浩二道歉后，没想到大部分网友都是挺的的，觉得他话说得虽然有点“难听”，但实际情况的确是如此，并非讨厌养狗，而是不少养狗的主人素质真的很一般，话糙理不糙。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><img style=\"margin: 10px auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\" alt=\"矢野浩二为在节目中称中国人没资格养狗道歉，网友：你说得对！\" src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/4ada000412d653131c5f\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">曾因在节目中一言葬送了在中国所有演出机会的还有张娜拉，其实现在看来，张娜拉当年所说的那句“没钱就去中国”，也的确是这么回事，很多日韩艺人不就是在国内不好混了，才来中国发展吗，在中国演出片酬比在他们国内高出几十倍几百倍。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><img style=\"margin: 10px auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\" alt=\"矢野浩二为在节目中称中国人没资格养狗道歉，网友：你说得对！\" src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/4adb00040ce3a70785ab\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><img style=\"margin: 10px auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\" alt=\"矢野浩二为在节目中称中国人没资格养狗道歉，网友：你说得对！\" src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/4ada0004131150cf86ff\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><img style=\"margin: 10px auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\" alt=\"矢野浩二为在节目中称中国人没资格养狗道歉，网友：你说得对！\" src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/4ae00001f3e429170149\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">娱少侠要说句公道话，浩二除了在日本节目中说过“中国人没资格养狗”，还说过很多中国的好话，曾在一次访谈类节目中，浩二赞中国观众非常捧场，大谈中国人友好，在中国工作时受到各种照顾。访谈中还播放了一段《天天向上》片段，这些在华演出经历，在浩二看来，都是引以为豪的。</p>', null);
INSERT INTO `art_content` VALUES ('53196240', '<p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">今年6月3日，义乌一家物流公司的员工在进行卸货作业时，<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">发现一件包裹外包装上写着“鞋子”，但实际份量却很重，远远超过鞋子的重量，非常可疑。</strong></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">工作人员按照规定对这个包裹开包检查，打开包裹后，层层叠叠还有七八层包装纸，<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">一层一层剥到最后，里面竟然是两块红色的砖头。</strong></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">“居然还有人花钱快递砖头？”</strong>工作人员觉得不对劲，再仔细一看，两块砖头间还夹藏着几个可疑的金属零件。他们立即向铁路义乌站派出所报了案。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">民警到了现场，发现这些金属零件很像是枪支的部件，<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">经过拼装，确认这是一把仿美国小熊马—柯尔特自动手枪，其中没有弹夹、子弹。</strong></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">据金华市公安司法鉴定中心鉴定，<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">这类枪以气体为动力发射，具有致伤力，近距离射击甚至可致人重伤。</strong></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><img style=\"margin: 10px auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\" alt=\"800多支枪流向全国25个省份，买家有医师、白领、高管、在校生\" src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/4ae300007f05dad3b2a4\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">藏在鞋盒里的砖头和仿真枪零件</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">是谁在偷运枪支？像这样的枪还有多少？是从哪里来的，又要被送到哪里去？</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">杭州铁路公安处抽调30余名精干警力成立专案组，顺着这条线索展开侦查……</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">12月3日，杭州铁路公安历时6个月，终于成功摧毁了一个利用网络、物流公司，集“供、运、销”于一体的贩枪网络，抓获贩枪骨干9名，其他各类嫌疑人174名，缴获仿真枪整枪145支、弓弩6把、弹弓枪1支，未组装枪支零部件369件，铅弹1.3万余颗。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><img style=\"margin: 10px auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\" alt=\"800多支枪流向全国25个省份，买家有医师、白领、高管、在校生\" src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/4ae0000337a580b4403c\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">警方查获的仿真枪械。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">据悉，这是近三年来全国铁路警方破获的最大一起涉枪案件，也是今年以来浙江省内最大的涉枪案件。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">造枪的是个玩具厂老板</strong></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">每种枪械都有零件模型</strong></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">通过缜密侦查，一个以网络为平台，层级分明、组织严密的贩枪网络逐渐浮出水面。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">专案组民警顺着资金走向一路追踪，<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">发现所有的枪支均来源于广东省汕头市，供货的是一个姓蔡的男人。</strong></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">7月10日，蔡被铁路警方抓获归案。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">蔡30岁出头，是当地一家玩具厂的老板，他售卖的玩具种类繁多，其中多是些不具有杀伤力的玩具枪械等。</strong></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">据蔡交代，他是从去年年底开始做买卖仿真枪支的生意的，<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">因为这种枪售价较高，利润也很可观，每支枪的售价基本都能翻一倍。</strong></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">民警说，蔡的枪支加工厂面积不大，在郊区一个隐蔽的地方，不同类型的枪械都有对应的零件模型，比如枪管、把手等，生产出来以后需要自己进行组装。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">除了手枪，加工厂里还生产长气枪、弓弩、弹弓枪等多种类型的枪支，这些枪都是铁铸的，都具有致伤力。</strong></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">化整为零伪装成普通包裹运输</strong></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">这些“黑火”从广东发往全国25个省份</strong></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">仿真枪支生产出来以后，怎么运送出去也是个问题。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">民警说，蔡的反侦察意识很强，<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">为了避开警方，他“化整为零”，把仿真枪支拆分成多个零件，伪装成普通的包裹进行寄递。而且，寄递单上填写的发货人姓名、地址、货物名称等都是伪造的。</strong></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">至于弹夹和子弹，也都是通过单独的包裹分开运输寄送的。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">由于铁路运输对货物的重量有要求，蔡就想到了加塞砖头的办法，既可以增加包裹重量，又能对枪支零件进行遮挡。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">通过这种方式，蔡制造的800多支枪支被发往全国各地。</strong></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">据警方查证，这些枪支流向全国25个省、自治区、直辖市，其中发往石家庄的最多，有500余支，浙江的杭州、金华、宁波、温州等地也均有涉及。</strong></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">通过网上聊天群发展下家</strong></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">“枪”、“子弹”等敏感字眼都用代号</strong></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">民警说，蔡主要是通过网上聊天群寻找下家进行交易的。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">蔡做玩具生意时，加入过一个有500余人的聊天群，之后，他时不时会在群里发布一些仿真枪的图片，对枪支有兴趣的人看到了，自然会私下和他联系，这时，蔡就暗示对方，自己这里有仿真枪可以交易。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">蔡和下家聊天很有默契，双方都不会提到“枪”、“子弹”等敏感字眼，而是直接报枪支型号。</strong>比如，仿美M1911A1型气动手枪简称“1911”，子弹则被称为“狗粮”。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">宁波男子任某就是蔡在浙江的下家之一，也是民警最先找到的嫌疑人，义乌物流公司员工发现的那些枪支，就是他寄送给其他买家的。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">任原本是做微商的，从小爱好玩枪，偶然在聊天群里发现有人贩卖仿真枪后，就开始做起了“二道贩子”，他先从蔡某处进货，之后通过微信朋友圈叫卖等方式，将这些枪支转卖给下级发货商或终端买家。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">据任交代，<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">自今年2月以来，他和仍在读大学的女友陈某租用了两间出租房，一间用于日常居住，一间专门用来存放枪支弹药。</strong></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">截至6月4日被抓，他和女友靠转卖枪支赚取差价，获利颇丰。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">案发后，民警从任的租处搜缴出仿真手枪48支、未组装零部件200余件。任说，他曾将枪支发往吉林、重庆、天津、武昌等多个地方，都是伪装成普通包裹运输的。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">买家有主任医师、白领、企业高管……</strong></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">购枪两支以上就将面临刑事处罚</strong></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">买弓弩也要受到行政处罚</strong></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">警方根据枪支流向对买家群体进行了调查，发现购买枪支的群体身份复杂，<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">其中不乏主任医师、白领、企业高管等，甚至还有一些是在校学生。</strong></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">民警说，从目前侦查的情况来看，大部分购买枪支的人都是因为对枪有一种特别的情结，购买后自行组装，或放在家里收藏，或用于打鸟、打酒瓶等娱乐活动的，暂时没有发现持枪者有危害他人人身安全的行为。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">不过，购买和持有枪支都属于违法行为。<strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">如果枪支经鉴定属于仿真枪的，购买一支，将受到行政处罚；购买两支以上，就要被追究刑事责任。</strong></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">根据法律规定，非法持有、私藏枪支、弹药的，处三年以下有期徒刑、拘役或者管制；情节严重的，处三年以上七年以下有期徒刑。</strong></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">弓弩虽然不属于枪支，但也是管制器械，购买持有者一旦被警方发现，也将受到行政处罚。</strong></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">都市快报记者 林琳 通讯员 韦士钊</strong></p>', null);
INSERT INTO `art_content` VALUES ('53196241', '<img style=\"margin: 10px auto; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; display: block; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\" alt=\"网易丁磊：我经常在京东上买东西，最重要的原因就是物流快\" src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/4a42000b2884077805e3\"/><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">2017年12月4日，浙江乌镇，第四届世界互联网大会举行“数字丝绸之路”国际合作分论坛现场，网易CEO丁磊（左一）、京东CEO刘强东（中）、小米科技CEO雷军（右一）同台探讨跨境电商。 视觉中国 图</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">“我经常在京东上买东西，原因就是除了正品以外，最重要的一件事情就是物流做得非常得快。你今天晚上买，第二天早上就到，早上买晚上就到。”12月4日，第四届世界互联网大会举行“数字丝绸之路”国际合作分论坛。出席该活动对话环节的网易董事局主席兼CEO丁磊毫不吝惜给京东董事局主席兼CEO刘强东捧场，连连称赞京东物流做得特别好。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">当天的对话，主要是围绕“跨境电商”展开，包括刘强东、丁磊以及小米科技董事长兼CEO雷军在内的多位企业家或互联网资深人士悉数到场。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">提到“买买买”，丁磊似乎很有感触。他坦言，过去四年，网易部署了大量采购人员“买全球”，再通过跨境电商的手段销售给中国消费者。未来几年，网易要做的是“卖全球”，即利用中国制造业的独特优势，生产出自己的产品，再出口到海外国家去。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">丁磊称，在“走过去”过程中，网易碰到一些挑战。比如海外用户在网易的平台下了单，怎样才能在成本可控的前提下，把商品完好快速地送到全世界消费者手上？对此，他提出，非常希望政府能够重视物流系统建设，发挥“国家队”作用，这必然会给“中国制造”出口带来好处。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">谈到“走出去”，刘强东也有很多想法。据他介绍，两年前，京东已进驻印尼，包括物流和配送，一整套体系都是企业自己建立的 。到2018年，相信印尼的京东会成为东南亚收入最高的电商公司。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">但另一方面，刘强东也很清醒。在他看来，如果京东进入欧美市场，就要和亚马逊竞争，倘若京东还卖欧美品牌，看不到任何所谓的优势。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">怎么办呢？刘强东认为，唯一的机会就是把众多中国优秀品牌集体带出去。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">他甚至考虑，刚开始，京东在欧美的网站全都只卖中国品牌，或中国生产制造的产品，比如说小米、华为等。每一个“中国制造”，都经过京东最苛刻的方式筛选，品质可以绝对保证，价格也更好，这样用十年、二十年的时间，京东也会得到欧美消费者的认可。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">同样是谈“走出去”，雷军也颇有发言权，分享了不少经验。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">据他介绍，目前小米的产品，已进入世界60多个国家，在13个国家排名前5位。在印度市场创造了一个奇迹，从最初进入到成为市场第一只用了3年时间。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">小米是怎么做到在海外市场如此红火？</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">雷军认为，这一轮中国产品出口都是靠品牌、靠技术、靠效率来支撑的。这也需要大家和传统观念作斗争，摒弃“便宜没好货“这种看法，同时也要承认东西做得好、成本一定高这一现实。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">至于成本高，为什么还能卖得很便宜？雷军表示，关键在于中间环节效率的提升，比如小米在国内起步的前四年，全部是靠电商完成市场销售。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">谈到最后，雷军也没忘和同行“联系感情”。看到京东在印尼做得风生水起，前段时间，他就和刘强东谈合作，希望在印尼以及周边国家尝试“电商先行”的模式，团结足够多的伙伴进一步拓展市场。</p>', null);
INSERT INTO `art_content` VALUES ('53196242', '<p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">先来看一个破碎的手机和一段聊天记录!</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><img style=\"margin: 10px auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\" alt=\"母亲在最后一刻喊出3个字 开车的儿子还在聊微信\" src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/4ae00001bf465f4383a7\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><img style=\"margin: 10px auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\" alt=\"母亲在最后一刻喊出3个字 开车的儿子还在聊微信\" src=\"http://p1.pstatp.com/large/4adf00023213c25a60de\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">这是12月2日傍晚，发生在G15沈海高速往上海方向1462K(过慈城服务区三公里处)的一起事故现场找到的手机，手机屏幕已经碎裂。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">22岁的相某，驾驶一辆轻型普通厢式货车追尾一辆槽罐半挂车，造成同乘的母亲受伤，后经医院抢救无效死亡。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">而事发时，驾驶员相某正是在玩手机，才导致悲剧的发生。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">据相某交待，他是下午装完货从宁波西收费站上的高速，打算前往上海奉贤。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">车上装的都是纸箱，有1吨多。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">在行驶至事发路段时，相某一直在用手机聊微信，和微信群里的朋友聊着晚上在上海见面的事情。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">在距离前车大概5米的样子，同乘的母亲、45岁的苏某大声提醒：“慢!慢!慢!”，等相某反应过来，往左打方向避让、踩刹车，这时已经来不及了。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">车头右侧与前车发生了猛烈的碰撞，苏某虽然坐在中间的位置而且还系了安全带，但是当场就已经失去了意识。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><img style=\"margin: 10px auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\" alt=\"母亲在最后一刻喊出3个字 开车的儿子还在聊微信\" src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/4add00039b2e2413ea55\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">后经报警，经消防破拆、交警和120救助，伤者在第一时间被送往就近医院救治，可惜最终由于伤势过重，未能抢救过来。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><img style=\"margin: 10px auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\" alt=\"母亲在最后一刻喊出3个字 开车的儿子还在聊微信\" src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/4ae00001bf48d31d9009\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">事故现场在一个小时后恢复正常通行。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">据前车司机刘某交待，他车上运载的是水泥，是从保国寺收费站上的高速，打算送往慈溪。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">事发时，突然听到后方一声巨响，就靠边停车了。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">然后就看到，车尾被后方一辆轻型货车追尾了，刘某赶紧报了警。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">相某在面对民警的时候，一次次留下了悔恨的泪水。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">目前，事故具体原因还在进一步调查当中。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">12月2日，是全国第六个交通安全宣传日，高速交警说，开车时使用手机的危险程度不言而喻，根据浙江省公安厅交通管理局的统计数据显示，去年浙江全省因交通事故死亡4187人，其中开车使用手机等影响安全行为导致的交通事故死亡达到1855人，占全省交通事故死亡总数的44.3%;今年1月至7月，我省交通管理部门查处的开车使用手机的违法行为高达14.8万起。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">高速交警说，高速公路车速快，行车情况复杂，在高速上打电话十分危险，但开车时盯着手机屏幕玩手机，相比之下就更危险了。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">今年6月起，浙江省内高速140多个卡点投入了一种新式监控“武器”，专拍开车玩手机的违法行为。仅仅在10月份，这套抓拍系统就拍到高速开车使用手机的违法行为达9000多起。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">通过这套系统，交警查到过一些很夸张的开车玩手机的情况：今年6月，甬台温高速往温州方向，一辆货车宁波牌照的货车经过这套抓拍系统时被拍下，交警发现，驾驶员一边在高速上开着车，两只手都离开了方向盘，捧着手机盯着看。交警事后了解到，这个司机因为开车开得太无聊，用手机在玩“斗地主”游戏，玩着玩着两只手一起来，方向盘也不要了。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">当你开车在看着手机的时候，谁又在看着路呢?</p>', null);
INSERT INTO `art_content` VALUES ('53196243', '<p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">中新社乌拉圭埃斯特角12月4日电 题：中国摩拜单车亮相乌拉圭：共享单车受追捧</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">中新社记者莫成雄</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">“摩拜单车太棒了！这种环保出行工具在拉美太受欢迎了，追捧者众，一定会大行其道。”</p><img style=\"margin: 10px auto; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; display: block; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\" alt=\"中国摩拜单车亮相乌拉圭：共享单车受追捧\" src=\"http://p1.pstatp.com/large/4a41000c973b3b62e13d\"/><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">资料图：摩拜单车在德国柏林投入运营。 中新社记者 彭大伟 摄</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">日前，在乌拉圭埃斯特角市举办的第十一届中国－拉美企业家高峰会上，中国摩拜单车甫一亮相，就受到众多来自拉美国家与会者的赞叹，对来自中国的环保共享单车纷纷竖起大拇指点赞。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">在摩拜单车演示现场，包括乌拉圭总统巴斯克斯在内的许多拉美与会者饶有兴趣地观看，并不时地向演示者提问。在观众好奇的目光下，演示者拿出手机轻轻一扫单车上的二维码，单车锁就自动打开了。接着，一些拉美人士在现场进行试骑，体验来自中国“智造”的环保共享单车。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">“这实在太神奇了，这种没有链条的摩拜单车动力来自哪里呢？车辆的位置又是如何定位的？”来自阿根廷的一位工商界人士不解地问。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">演示者介绍说，“共享单车的很多奥秘都藏在这个锁中，它就像一个没有屏幕的智能手机，里面装有定位系统、移动报警系统、充电系统、用户交互系统等，这是一种运用物联网、云计算和大数据技术的分享经济模式，蕴涵着很多创新的高科技手段，共享单车的诞生带来了一场出行革命。”</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">与会者反响热烈，啧啧称奇。“无桩停车真是太便捷了，拉美人喜欢绿色出行方式，拉美太需要这种环保共享单车了。”“摩拜单车使用手机支付的方式快捷先进，期望中国摩拜单车尽快进入拉美市场。”“拉美自行车售价高，共享自行车市场巨大，中国的共享单车在拉美发展前景广阔。”</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">乌拉圭投资和出口促进局顾问桑潇逸对记者说，“近年来在中国非常火爆的共享单车受到拉美人的青睐和追捧。相信共享单车这个项目在拉美一定会有市场，会大有作为的。”</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">摩拜单车副总裁杨众杰表示，我们热切希望把这种智能、环保、方便的智能共享单车出行方式带给拉美当地民众，同时也愿意为拉美建设智慧新城市提供基于物联网和大数据的绿色智能出行解决方案。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">目前摩拜单车活跃在全球200个城市，在全世界运营超过700万辆单车，每天提供超过3000万次骑行，拥有超过2亿注册用户，使摩拜单车成为全球最大的智能共享出行平台。摩拜单车已在中国和其他11个国家提供智能共享单车服务，包括新加坡、英国、意大利、荷兰、马来西亚、泰国、韩国、日本、澳大利亚、美国以及德国。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">杨众杰透露，2017年6月，摩拜单车荣获世界自然基金会(WWF)“气候创行者可持续城市交通特别奖”，表彰其创新技术带来积极影响和促进可持续交通。同年9月，摩拜单车被《财富》杂志评为“2017年50家改变世界的公司”之一。(完)</p>', null);
INSERT INTO `art_content` VALUES ('53196244', '<p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">法制晚报·看法新闻（记者 岳三猛）又一个小官巨贪！成都土地储备中心原副主任刘光荣（正处级）日前因受贿4000多万被判有期徒刑15年。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">看法新闻记者注意到，此人的女婿、出生于1982年的罗存刚也因窝藏、转移其中2050万元而一审获刑5年，并被处罚金200万元。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><img style=\"margin: 10px auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\" alt=\"老丈人受贿4000万，女婿因为做这件事也进去了\" src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/4ae6000006737cdc41e5\"/></p><h1 style=\"margin: 36px 0px 22px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; line-height: 32px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 24px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 700; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">上诉后重审，罚金多了70万</strong></h1><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">公开资料显示，刘光荣2004年至2014年12月之间，分别担任金堂县国土局局长、成都市土地整治中心主任、成都市土地储备中心副主任等职，是个名副其实的“土地爷”。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">也正是利用这方面的职务便利，此人在项目招投标、购买耕地指标、工程承揽等大肆敛财，竟然共计4130万元人民币、20万元港币、一辆奥迪轿车、一辆途锐越野车、一只卡地亚手表。最终，其因受贿罪获刑15年、罚金200万，赃款赃物全部上缴国库。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">必须要指出的是，他们家身陷囹圄的并非仅刘光荣一个人，还有其女婿、现年仅35岁的罗存刚。今年8月31日，攀枝花中院一审认定，罗存刚明知2050万元是犯罪所得，仍然窝藏、转移，触犯掩饰、隐瞒犯罪所得罪，判处其有期徒刑5年，并处罚金200万元。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">看法新闻记者发现，其实早在2015年2月，罗存刚就已被刑拘，而且同年12月因犯掩饰、隐瞒犯罪所得罪，被攀枝花中院一审判处有期徒刑五年，并处罚金130万元。只是罗存刚不服提出上诉，省高院认为部分事实不清，裁定发回重新审判。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">相比较之下，罗存刚的罪名和刑期没有发生变化，只是罚金数由130万增至200万。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">梳理整个收钱的过程可以发现，罗存刚共替自己的老丈人出头3次，分别从商人处拿到500万元、250万元、1300万元，即总计2050万元。这些钱要么是买了别墅、楼房，要么是用来炒股理财，还有的则开公司或者日常开支。</p><h1 style=\"margin: 36px 0px 22px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; line-height: 32px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 24px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 700; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">曾化名到商人处拿贿赂款</strong></h1><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">他第一次帮岳父拿钱，发生在2008年。当时刘光荣所在单位想买土地指标，商人邓某获悉后前往洽谈。此时，刘光荣说其他人卖指标都要给钱，并要其给500万元好处费。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">此后，罗存刚登场了。他按照岳父的要求，不仅买了新的手机号，还搞了个假名字，并自称是刘光荣的好友。没有深究的邓某分300万和200万两次，装进纸箱子给了罗存刚。利用这笔钱，他以小姨子的名字买了一套房。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><img style=\"margin: 10px auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\" alt=\"老丈人受贿4000万，女婿因为做这件事也进去了\" src=\"http://p1.pstatp.com/large/4ae30000433a435803f3\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); text-transform: none; line-height: 16px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">（资料图）</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">至于第二次收钱，刘光荣似乎胆子大了不少。当商人邹某拿到几个土地整理工程后，2010年，刘光荣打电话称，其女婿罗存刚要买房子，让准备250万元。于是，这次罗存刚没有化名，而是直接收钱，完事儿后按照指示给小姨子买了300多平米的大房，价值500多万。</span><br/></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">看法新闻记者注意到，第三次收的钱最多，达到1300万。先是在2011年，商人蔡某不仅拿到了工程，还得到付款等方面的帮助，于是决定送刘光荣300万。罗志刚拿到后，老丈人也没说什么，只是让他拿去用。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">两年多后，刘光荣再次找到蔡某，称有个5亿多的项目想不想做。商人当然满口答应，便许诺到时分成，即给1000万。于是，在成都高威体育公园，罗存刚收到3个水果箱，每个箱里装有100万元现金。此后，他又陆续收到7个装有100万元现金的箱子。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">罗存刚供述称，在拿1000万元的后几次时，他发现这些钱可能存在问题。所以当岳父再让其拿钱时，他拒绝了。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">然而，错误已经铸就，哪儿能如此轻易回头，等待他的是法律制裁。</p>', '20170014,20170013');
INSERT INTO `art_content` VALUES ('53196245', '<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://p1.pstatp.com/large/4adc0003105d2b3541cf\" alt=\"孙俪的悲剧：4次身价过亿，次次都泡汤了\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; display: block; margin: 10px auto;\"/></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">都说事不过三，如果四次呢？要么愤怒，要么伤透了心。戏里的女王，股市的韭菜。这就是孙俪。文投控股突然说，海润影视我们不收了，看来孙俪的上市梦又黄了。究竟是为什么呢？</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://p1.pstatp.com/large/4adc000311ff206fb226\" alt=\"孙俪的悲剧：4次身价过亿，次次都泡汤了\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; display: block; margin: 10px auto;\"/></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">19岁那一年，孙俪完成了人生的天使轮融资，投资人自然是海润影视，一部《玉观音》令孙俪一炮而红。尽管后来孙俪跟海润影视合作的戏份越来越少，可孙俪对海润影视深有情感，反过来投资成了海润影视的股东。在拍摄《幸福像花儿一样》时，孙俪将自己IPO给邓超了，之后，孙俪的人生开挂了，《甄嬛传》、《芈月传》令她大红大紫。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">有一句话说，情场得意，商场失意。孙俪投资的海润影视从IPO到借壳，再到资产重组，每一次孙俪的账面都身价过亿，可每一次高兴几个月就失败。在乐视影业最火热的时候，夫妻两下注五千万，没想到最终还是失败了。这不，文投控股两个月前说收购海润影视，没想到谈了两个月，还是黄了。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">其实文投控股这次重组，涉及了包括海润影视之外的其余两家标的公司，悦凯影视和宏宇天润。那么就目前而言明显海润影视被剔除在外，剩下的两家公司重组仍在进行。悦凯影视是一家主要从事影视剧制作与发行以及艺人经纪业务；宏宇天润是一家专注于IP全维度运营的文化传媒公司，很明显这一轮的PK，海润影视出局，孙俪的女股神梦又泡汤了！</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://p1.pstatp.com/large/4ade0002c75d9dff6b80\" alt=\"孙俪的悲剧：4次身价过亿，次次都泡汤了\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; display: block; margin: 10px auto;\"/></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">在2016年3月1日的时候德林社微信公众号（ID:delinshe）就曾发文《孙俪想演股神， A股只有祥林嫂》，炒股遇到股灾的孙俪，在决定当股东的时候没想到刚要重组上A股，结果临门一脚，擦A股门框而过。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/4ada000314995a3f68df\" alt=\"孙俪的悲剧：4次身价过亿，次次都泡汤了\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; display: block; margin: 10px auto;\"/></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/4adb00030f8fd70570a7\" alt=\"孙俪的悲剧：4次身价过亿，次次都泡汤了\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; display: block; margin: 10px auto;\"/></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://p1.pstatp.com/large/4ade0002c453ed9a6fca\" alt=\"孙俪的悲剧：4次身价过亿，次次都泡汤了\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; display: block; margin: 10px auto;\"/></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">孙俪喜欢绿色，喜欢玩具熊，这是股市的大忌。孙俪现在的戏路越来越宽，可海润影视这么多年上市怎么就那么难呢？德林社微信公众号（ID:delinshe）认为：海润影视的起家就是靠破案等题材，绝大多数片子都是给卫视量身定做，这种片子成本高，收益率低，很难获得网络平台的高溢价。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">德林社微信公众号（ID:delinshe）发现：海润影视的传统模式正在失去竞争力，2015年盈利不到2000万，2016年前三个季度利润不到60万，可2016年11月，海润影视的估值已经到27亿，要卖给文投控股，估值肯定会更高，现在文投控股账面资金才29亿，将近20亿是定增的专项资金，怎么收购海润？就算继续增发，像文投控股那样综合类影视文化上市公司，收海润势必要进行三年的业绩对赌，海润影视拿什么赌？</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">海润影视从IPO，到借壳，再到出售，可以窥见海润的下坡路越走越远。海润影视只是中国影视转型的一个缩影，凡是那一种抱残守缺的传统企业，一旦失去战略上的转型先机，上市的梦只会越来越远。面对海润影视上市再次流产，也许，股民们会说，指屁吹灯，没希望。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">无论是从赵薇还是孙俪，贾跃亭还是孙宏斌，德林社微信公众号（ID:delinshe）一直为大家揭露和诠释着金融圈里的故事，马云也好、马化腾也罢，我们其实每个人都在于这经济市场联系着。多了解一些财经知识，无论是炒股投资，还是生意场，对我们都百利而无一害，欢迎大家搜索关注微信公众号德林社（ID:delinshe，为您揭秘更多资本的真相！</p>', null);
INSERT INTO `art_content` VALUES ('53196246', '<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">12月4日，是国家宪法日。当天上午，江苏省高级法院举行新闻发布会，通报全省法院涉民生领域职务犯罪审判工作情况，并发布了10起典型案例，其中包括一其学校校长挪用公款、受贿案。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">值得注意的是，该案涉及学校多人，是一起窝案。期间，其挪用公款之巨，达到3244万元。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">裁判文书网公布的刑事判决书显示，温东屏，男，1962年12月25日出生于江苏省常熟市，大学文化，原系常熟市周行学校校长。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">公开资料显示，常熟市周行学校位于常熟市的东郊，2000年9月，常熟市周行中心小学并入，成为一所九年一贯制学校。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">2016年3月2日，温东屏因涉嫌犯受贿罪，经江苏常熟市人民检察院决定刑事拘留，同年3月15日被批准逮捕。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">判决书及典型案例材料均显示，温东屏在担任常熟市周行学校校长期间，伙同常熟市周行学校原副校长孟某、原出纳会计吴某、主办会计叶某、原主办会计邵某，经预谋后分别利用各自职务便利，在管理学校收费、日常资金的过程中，于2008年9月至2015年10月间，多次挪用常熟市周行学校开学时收取的教育保育费、教辅用书费、伙食费以及在编不在岗教师工资等款项，用于开具银行个人存单、购买理财产品等，共计挪用公款人民币3244元，所得收益共计人民币86781元由上述人员进行私分。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">此外，温东屏还利用职务便利，在负责学校课桌椅、玩具、牛奶等物资采购，组织学生旅游等过程中，为他人谋取利益，于2009年11月至2016年1月间，多次收受他人财物，共计15.66万元。案发后，其家属代为退出非法所得20万元。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">据江苏省高院提供的相关材料介绍，这起案件还体现了这类职务犯罪案件的特点，即“案中有案，案外有案，侦破一案带出一串、端出一窝”。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">常熟市某商贸公司法定代表人徐某标先后多次分别向温东屏等当地5所学校校长行贿9万余元，通过相关校长采取挤占、克扣学生伙食费的方式，用于购买其奶制品等食品。判决书显示，温东屏收受贿赂一万。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">据此，2016年12月，常熟市人民法院对温东屏以挪用公款罪判处有期徒刑五年，以受贿罪判处有期徒刑二年，并处罚金人民币12万元，数罪并罚，决定执行有期徒刑五年六个月，并处罚金人民币12万元。受贿款人民币15.66万元，予以没收，上缴国库；挪用公款非法所得人民币4.3万元，发还被害单位。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">本案的典型意义在于，是教育领域发生的职务犯罪典型案件。温东屏作为学校校长，肩负着教书育人的重大责任，理应带头遵守法律，清正校园风气，为师生创造良好的教学、学习环境，但其无视国家法律法规，在行使学校教学管理、物资采购等职权过程中，收取他人财物，同时与下属共同挪用学校资金从事营利活动，“既侵害学校师生权益，也助长了教育领域的不正之风，损害了教育工作者的良好形象，更对教育事业造成严重的危害”，应依法予以惩处。</p>', null);
INSERT INTO `art_content` VALUES ('53196247', '<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/4ad90003bca28e7efb99\" alt=\"10岁女生偷钱买漫画书内容露骨 书店就在学校附近\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; display: block; margin: 10px auto;\"/></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">10岁女生偷钱买漫画书，内容露骨。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">西部网讯（陕西广播电视台《都市快报》记者 张刚）10岁的女孩正处在青春期，家住西安南郊的一位李女士，发现上四年级的女儿，最近迷恋上了一种漫画书，可这书的内容让李女士有些担忧。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">李女士：“《天降贤淑男》，这种书她能看吗？都是亲呀抱呀，而且还有一些亲密的动作。”</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">李女士说，这本书是老师从自己10岁的女儿手里没收的。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://p1.pstatp.com/large/4adc00013a1de500047e\" alt=\"10岁女生偷钱买漫画书内容露骨 书店就在学校附近\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; display: block; margin: 10px auto;\"/></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">李女士：“包里有七八本那种漫画小说，我把书翻了一遍，发现里边的内容是不堪入目，让人看了扎眼。这些成年人看了都会羞愧得很，不要说四年级的学生了，第一次我就扔掉了。”</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">本想着孩子不会再买，可是……</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">李女士 ：“前天晚上，孩子睡着了，我在她书包又发现了六本这样的书。”</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">两个月的时间，女儿就背着她买了五百多块钱的漫画书，沉迷其中的孩子学习成绩也大幅下滑。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">李女士 ：“从班上的前十名掉到快三十名了。”</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">一本书少说十几块钱，李女士平时除了给孩子几块钱的吃饭钱，并没有给太多，那么买书的钱是哪来的呢？</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">李女士 ：“她说从我包里偷偷拿的钱。”</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">记者了解到，卖这种书的书店就开在学校门前100米以内。李女士也希望相关的职能部门能到这家店查一查，可不能让更多孩子再沉迷其中了。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://p1.pstatp.com/large/4adb00013d1bb361608c\" alt=\"10岁女生偷钱买漫画书内容露骨 书店就在学校附近\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; display: block; margin: 10px auto;\"/></p>', null);
INSERT INTO `art_content` VALUES ('53196248', '<p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">作为一款开放世界的沙盒游戏，《我的世界》吸引玩家的就是它多种多样自由的玩法，你在里面可以变成任何你想变成的生活。然而，在这样一个充满神奇的方块世界里，也藏着一些细思极恐的事情，看完真的一身冷汗……</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">1.关于HIM的都市传说</strong></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">说HIM是我的世界里最可怕的生物，应该没有人会反对吧？传说它是一位玩家被吸入游戏中在游戏里永远注视着你的一举一动的存在。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><img style=\"margin: 10px auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\" alt=\"不看不知道！我的世界里那些细思极恐的事情，看完你还敢玩吗？\" src=\"http://p9.pstatp.com/large/4ae30000188ad476dd79\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">有时候它还会突然出现在你的面前，像素眼变成白色的人眼，让你陷入恐慌——至于这位玩家的本体？当然是三次元死亡咯~</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">不过，游戏方对此已经做过了辟谣，就是个都市传说而已啦，但是，讲真，在游戏中看到HIM，你真的不会感觉背脊发凉吗？</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">2.玩麦块注定单身？</strong></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><img style=\"margin: 10px auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\" alt=\"不看不知道！我的世界里那些细思极恐的事情，看完你还敢玩吗？\" src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/4ae1000020bfbc157ac4\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">很多人喜欢用方块做出各种各样鬼斧神工的东西，也有一些人会用方块拼出自己心仪女孩的模样，然后开开心心的去献宝。然而，如果你真的这样做了的话，那么你必将受到单身的惩罚！！！</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">3.JJ怪</strong></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><img style=\"margin: 10px auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\" alt=\"不看不知道！我的世界里那些细思极恐的事情，看完你还敢玩吗？\" src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/4ae1000020beaf6b9285\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">对于新手来说，遇到JJ怪简直就是噩梦，小心肝都要抖三抖！</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">4.失落的文明?</strong></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">在这个无限创造的世界里，你可以创造出各种各样的不可能，但是你有没有想过，在这个高度自由的背后，到底隐藏着什么样的秘密?</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><img style=\"margin: 10px auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\" alt=\"不看不知道！我的世界里那些细思极恐的事情，看完你还敢玩吗？\" src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/4add0004ae32d75b548a\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">尘封的宝箱中为何会有骸骨和腐肉？海里钓上来的为何尽是人的物品？为什么会有隐藏着杀人于无形的红石机关和嗜血的僵尸？欢迎收看《走近科学》之我的世界这里空无一人。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><img style=\"margin: 10px auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\" alt=\"不看不知道！我的世界里那些细思极恐的事情，看完你还敢玩吗？\" src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/4ade0004a0874d96dfb7\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">是的，这里曾经有很多像史蒂夫一样的“人”，他们创造了璀璨的文明。然而，满眼数不尽的雄伟建筑，却空无一人。而四处游荡的僵尸们，看上去都好像是史蒂夫的先祖……</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><img style=\"margin: 10px auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\" alt=\"不看不知道！我的世界里那些细思极恐的事情，看完你还敢玩吗？\" src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/4ae00002d1e2c10c829e\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">而且，残暴的怪物们只攻击人形的史蒂夫和村民，普通的动物却安然无恙。所以，这到底是为什么？</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">5.走不出去的地狱</strong></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">玩过地狱模式的人一定都知道这样一种说法吧：进入地狱后，一定要保护好传送门，这样才能出去，否则将一辈子困在里面。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><img style=\"margin: 10px auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\" alt=\"不看不知道！我的世界里那些细思极恐的事情，看完你还敢玩吗？\" src=\"http://p1.pstatp.com/large/4ae30000188d785ab161\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">6.僵尸会夜袭小屋</strong></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">每到夜幕降临的时候，怪物就开始出门，其中最令人最为恐惧的莫过于僵尸。作为游戏中一种常见的攻击型亡灵生物，他们绝对是生存模式夜晚里让人非常恐惧的存在，每天晚上一直在你的房子周围旋转跳跃，真的有点可怕……</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><img style=\"margin: 10px auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\" alt=\"不看不知道！我的世界里那些细思极恐的事情，看完你还敢玩吗？\" src=\"http://p9.pstatp.com/large/4ae00002d1e54bf9cfe9\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">7.停不下来的11号唱片</strong></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">传说这是一个矿工在矿井里被怪物追逐，最后死于末影人的一段记录。因此，在播放的时候，你会听到疾跑、打火石的声音，还有不安的呼吸声、挣扎的声音以及各种奇怪的吠叫声等等。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><img style=\"margin: 10px auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\" alt=\"不看不知道！我的世界里那些细思极恐的事情，看完你还敢玩吗？\" src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/4adf000345a22f51a4ed\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">8.白天不鸟你晚上蹲你的蜘蛛</strong></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">蜘蛛在白天不会主动攻击你，除非它在夜晚就已经锁定你了。但是还有一种意外情况，就是蜘蛛晚上在你家蹲点，这样的话白天也照样会攻击你。当你使用隐身药水攻击它的时候，你依然能够看到它的眼睛哦！</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><img style=\"margin: 10px auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\" alt=\"不看不知道！我的世界里那些细思极恐的事情，看完你还敢玩吗？\" src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/4ae200001ec09d8c6887\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">9.掉苹果的ID？</strong></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">如果你把你的游戏ID修改成为Notch，如果你死亡后，就会掉落一个苹果，亲测有效哦！</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><img style=\"margin: 10px auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\" alt=\"不看不知道！我的世界里那些细思极恐的事情，看完你还敢玩吗？\" src=\"http://p1.pstatp.com/large/4ae200001ec1092d0242\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">10.怕仙人掌的怪物？</strong></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">在自己的身边放置四个仙人掌，然后再用钓竿去钓怪物，那么怪物就会被仙人掌扎死……emmm，有点萌是怎么回事？</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">11.你以为的死亡，并不是死亡</strong></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><img style=\"margin: 10px auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\" alt=\"不看不知道！我的世界里那些细思极恐的事情，看完你还敢玩吗？\" src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/4ade0004a08afc2b8646\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">所以啊，Minecraft还是玩联机版的好……</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><img style=\"margin: 10px auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\" alt=\"不看不知道！我的世界里那些细思极恐的事情，看完你还敢玩吗？\" src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/4ae1000020c5b5b2ab81\"/></p>', null);
INSERT INTO `art_content` VALUES ('53196249', '<h1 style=\"margin: 36px 0px 22px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; line-height: 32px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 24px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 700; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">12月5日，《绝地求生》官方微博公布了新的载具——皮卡。</h1><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><img style=\"margin: 10px auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\" alt=\"《绝地求生》微博爆料新载具上线，然而评论区却因为55开炸了\" src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/4ae400018d442ca33e06\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">这辆车将在未来将开放的沙漠地图中刷新。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">根据图片来看，皮卡车舱内有两个乘员位置；而后面比较大的挎斗是否可以坐人，是否可以架设M249，都还需要在游戏内实际测试。<br/></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">而皮卡上的探路灯，也为夜战地图留足了悬念。</p><h1 style=\"margin: 36px 0px 22px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; line-height: 32px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 24px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 700; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">然而，评论区却炸出了另一朵烟花：</h1><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">最近，55开外挂消息甚嚣尘上。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">而《绝地求生》的最新微博，则成了众多网友的战场，让我们看看热评都说了些什么吧：<br/></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><img style=\"margin: 10px auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\" alt=\"《绝地求生》微博爆料新载具上线，然而评论区却因为55开炸了\" src=\"http://p9.pstatp.com/large/4ae30001de828e7b29a3\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><img style=\"margin: 10px auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\" alt=\"《绝地求生》微博爆料新载具上线，然而评论区却因为55开炸了\" src=\"http://p9.pstatp.com/large/4ae60001a436a1399619\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><img style=\"margin: 10px auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\" alt=\"《绝地求生》微博爆料新载具上线，然而评论区却因为55开炸了\" src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/4ae20001e6ef31fb15f7\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><img style=\"margin: 10px auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\" alt=\"《绝地求生》微博爆料新载具上线，然而评论区却因为55开炸了\" src=\"http://p1.pstatp.com/large/4ae000049acfcce69938\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><img style=\"margin: 10px auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\" alt=\"《绝地求生》微博爆料新载具上线，然而评论区却因为55开炸了\" src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/4ae40001929d086bfa77\"/></p>', null);
INSERT INTO `art_content` VALUES ('53196250', '<p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">要说现在最火的游戏种类非TPS（第三人称射击游戏）莫属，而且在最近这一个多月的时间里大有赶超MOBA品类的趋势。王者荣耀的风光不再，游戏下载榜榜首的位置始终在几个吃鸡手游中交替。国内手游市场即将迎来新的转折期，王者荣耀一家独大的局面或将改变，这里面首当其冲的挑战者便是来自网易的《荒野行动》。<br/></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><img style=\"margin: 10px auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\" alt=\"《荒野行动》这些彩蛋你全都见到了吗？最后一个套路简直不要太深\" src=\"http://p1.pstatp.com/large/4ae30000235d1261d094\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">网易出品的游戏虽然氪金程度很高，但是游戏的品质还是非常有保证的。最近连续推出的两款吃鸡手游《荒野行动》和《终结者2：审判日》更是长期占据免费游戏下载榜第一的位置，即使是背靠腾讯的《光荣使命》，上线几天后，也再次被《荒野行动》拉下马来，可见玩家们对其认可程度。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><img style=\"margin: 10px auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\" alt=\"《荒野行动》这些彩蛋你全都见到了吗？最后一个套路简直不要太深\" src=\"http://p9.pstatp.com/large/4ae00002dd62a4455870\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">提到网易出品的这款《荒野行动》，之所以能够取得如今的成绩，完全依赖其本身过硬的品质和稳定流畅的游戏体验。它没有《小米枪战》上线时的大型发布会，也没有《光荣使命》预约时的饥饿营销，却凭借其良好的口碑在玩家中不断发酵和传播，最终赢得玩家们的喜爱。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><img style=\"margin: 10px auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\" alt=\"《荒野行动》这些彩蛋你全都见到了吗？最后一个套路简直不要太深\" src=\"http://p9.pstatp.com/large/4ade0004ac35a342c517\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">在《荒野行动》中，这些细节的彩蛋也可以看出游戏策划的投入。随时有给自家打广告的成分，但是丝毫不显生硬。首先是游戏中的空投，被喷上了网易严选的字样。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><img style=\"margin: 10px auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\" alt=\"《荒野行动》这些彩蛋你全都见到了吗？最后一个套路简直不要太深\" src=\"http://p1.pstatp.com/large/4add00049bc13da719a4\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">其次，在一些建筑物外面也会见到带有网易考拉LOGO样式的箱子。<br/></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><img style=\"margin: 10px auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\" alt=\"《荒野行动》这些彩蛋你全都见到了吗？最后一个套路简直不要太深\" src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/4ae00002bfdb644f0953\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">此外，还有标着网易云音乐的废弃大巴车。<br/></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><img style=\"margin: 10px auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\" alt=\"《荒野行动》这些彩蛋你全都见到了吗？最后一个套路简直不要太深\" src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/4ae30000069fdde7430f\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">而套路最深，也最让玩家们津津乐道的就是游戏中的一种载具——补漏车。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><img style=\"margin: 10px auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\" alt=\"《荒野行动》这些彩蛋你全都见到了吗？最后一个套路简直不要太深\" src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/4ae00002c00a0d4efe84\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">在吃鸡类游戏中载具随处可见，而汽车类载具通常是有鸣笛功能的，而这两防水补漏面包车的鸣笛功能更是还原了防水补漏的原声配音，这一魔性的设置让很多玩家按到根本停不下来，也因此变成快递箱。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">同时，在车身后面有一个电话号码，相信大家都在影视剧中见过剧中的电话号码，通常为空号，不过依然会有好奇心很强的人去尝试拨通。同样，这辆防水补漏车后面的号码也有很多玩家尝试拨打，这也是网易《荒野行动》里面套路最深的一个设计。这个电话就是用来“防水补漏”的，不过是给玩家“防水补漏”的，没错，这个就是《荒野行动》官方客服热线。拨通这个号码之后，可以进行BUG提交，账号解封等一系列功能，如此细节处理，确实秒杀其他同类游戏。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">玩家们觉得呢？在下方留言讨论，说说你在《荒野行动》中遇到的那些奇人异事吧！</p>', null);
INSERT INTO `art_content` VALUES ('53196251', '<p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">游戏主角在你印象中都是什么样的？是奎爷那样的霸气无匹，还是但丁那样的狂妄潇洒，亦或是薛帕德那样的淡定冷静？如果游戏主角全都这么强大，可能游戏世界就不会如此丰富多彩了吧。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">今天小编为大家带来的是游戏里最脆弱的游戏主角，他们基本都是平凡的肉身，有些一碰就挂，有些被轻松小怪爆掉……但正是因为他们的不强大，才体现出了游戏的乐趣，也让玩家能感受到成长的意义。下面就一起来看看这些可怜的主角们吧！</p><hr style=\"background: rgb(237, 64, 64); margin: 40px auto; padding: 0px; border: currentColor; border-image: none; width: 64px; height: 4px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; overflow: visible; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: content-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"/><h1 style=\"margin: 36px 0px 22px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; line-height: 32px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 24px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 700; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">No.10 《GTA》系列</h1><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">其实在本榜单里，GTA系列各主角还算比较强的了。虽然都是普通人，不过都是退伍军人、街头混混这种级别的。不过就算这样，他们在GTA的世界里也占不到丝毫优势，徒手格斗得打半天，各种持枪的能力也算及格而已，跑几步就得喘半天，不穿防弹衣也死的飞快。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">其实他们还是挺厉害的，各种汽车、飞机手到擒来，对吧？</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">对，我知道，GTA是写实的游戏。也许正是因为主角的普通，我们才能见识到他们真正强大的内心吧。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><img style=\"margin: 10px auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\" alt=\"盘点游戏史上最弱鸡的十大游戏主角\" src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/3e610001f0ff7d593f54\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); text-transform: none; line-height: 16px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"></p><h1 style=\"margin: 36px 0px 22px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; line-height: 32px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 24px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 700; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">No.9 《寂静岭》系列</h1><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">这里的主角就真正是普通人了，甚至连弱女子也必须为了生存而奋斗下去。这些主角几乎毫无特殊之处，甚至你可以想象你自己进入寂静岭的世界是个什么模样。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">他们会用基本的武器，只能用可怜的力量战胜那一个个无脸女护士等怪物。相比同类游戏《死亡空间》和《生存之旅》，寂静岭的主角弱了不是一星半点。而这些，正是这款生存类恐怖游戏的最佳要素。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><img style=\"margin: 10px auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\" alt=\"盘点游戏史上最弱鸡的十大游戏主角\" src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/3e610001f03d38993740\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); text-transform: none; line-height: 16px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"></p><h1 style=\"margin: 36px 0px 22px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; line-height: 32px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 24px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 700; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">NO.8 《</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">心灵杀手》</span></h1><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">一个作家除了写文章还能干啥？只会用自家的那种小左轮手枪，偶尔用用打猎时候的猎枪而已。配上一个手电筒和几个烟花，完了，出去面对大批的黑暗吧。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">这就是游戏《心灵杀手》的主角艾伦·维克。一个普通到不能再普通的主角，拯救他的不是抢和炮，是外界的灯光和内心的光明。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><img style=\"margin: 10px auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\" alt=\"盘点游戏史上最弱鸡的十大游戏主角\" src=\"http://p9.pstatp.com/large/3e5f0001f896d743031b\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); text-transform: none; line-height: 16px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"></p><h1 style=\"margin: 36px 0px 22px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; line-height: 32px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 24px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 700; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">No.7 普林尼——《普林尼：我能当主角吗？》</h1><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">本作是一款很有意思的动作游戏，主角是魔界战记中的普林尼，没错，就是那个呆呆肥肥的企鹅。由于这个有趣的设定，本游戏还是受到了不少玩家，特别是魔界战记fans的期待。本作是比较传统的横版过关游戏，不过也有着自己鲜明的特色，那就是这个主角弱爆啦！</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">你需要用1000条企鹅的尸体来堆积出你的胜利！</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><img style=\"margin: 10px auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\" alt=\"盘点游戏史上最弱鸡的十大游戏主角\" src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/3e5f0001f96d211855d3\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); text-transform: none; line-height: 16px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"></p><h1 style=\"margin: 36px 0px 22px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; line-height: 32px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 24px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 700; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">No.6 《地狱边境》</h1><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">这小男孩就更悲催了，连一把武器都没有，只能跑跑跳跳，靠智力解决问题。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">只要进入陷阱，他几乎就是不堪一击的，完全秒杀，各位玩的时候可得小心了。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><img style=\"margin: 10px auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\" alt=\"盘点游戏史上最弱鸡的十大游戏主角\" src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/3e5e0004515bb25931c4\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); text-transform: none; line-height: 16px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"></p><h1 style=\"margin: 36px 0px 22px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; line-height: 32px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 24px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 700; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">No.5 《失忆症：黑暗后裔》</h1><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">也许有很多朋友没有玩过这款游戏，这游戏的主角到底是啥水平？</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">简单的说，很脆弱，毫无战斗能力，遇到敌人只能躲，从头到尾只有一盏煤油灯为伴。好歹你也捅捅人啊！</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><img style=\"margin: 10px auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\" alt=\"盘点游戏史上最弱鸡的十大游戏主角\" src=\"http://p9.pstatp.com/large/3e620001e827764ced23\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); text-transform: none; line-height: 16px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"></p><h1 style=\"margin: 36px 0px 22px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; line-height: 32px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 24px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 700; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">No.4 《零》系列</h1><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">作为鬼魂向的恐怖游戏，这款《零》也算是奇葩中的奇葩了，每代的主角都是音轻体柔易推倒的妹子，而她们的武器居然是照相机。照相机！你没看错，她们用照相机来记录和鬼魂的美好瞬间。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">开玩笑，其实妹子们是用照相机来驱魂的。不过这些柔弱的妹子还是很容易被鬼魂下一跳的。看来照相机的确是神器！</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><img style=\"margin: 10px auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\" alt=\"盘点游戏史上最弱鸡的十大游戏主角\" src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/3e65000058913063926a\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); text-transform: none; line-height: 16px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"></p><h1 style=\"margin: 36px 0px 22px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; line-height: 32px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 24px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 700; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">No.3 比尔、兰斯——《魂斗罗》</h1><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">所以说不得不佩服当年游戏玩家的坚韧程度呀，这样的游戏在今天看来就是难到变态的级别。这么强壮的两个裸男，被子弹蹭一下，被敌人碰一下，立马到底而亡。要是你不作弊的话，也就三条命够你潇洒。要是放在今天，绝对是碰一下，然后主角马上躲墙壁后面喘两口气，血就回满了！</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">所以大家知道上上下下左右左右BABA有多重要了吧！不过人家还是贵为地球最强战士！</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><img style=\"margin: 10px auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\" alt=\"盘点游戏史上最弱鸡的十大游戏主角\" src=\"http://p1.pstatp.com/large/3e600001c3e6f4c521f7\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); text-transform: none; line-height: 16px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"></p><h1 style=\"margin: 36px 0px 22px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; line-height: 32px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 24px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 700; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">No.2 克里斯、里昂、吉尔等——《生化危机1/2/3》</h1><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">当《生化危机》还是一个恐怖生存类游戏的时候，里面的主角真是弱小到可怕的地步，而整体的游戏氛围一没有一处不在突出这一点。少的可怜的弹药，满地图找不到的草药，略反人类的操作，以及逆天到爆的怪兽！当年一个hunter就能让你痛不欲生了，更不要说复仇女神这样的怪物了！</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">看看现在呢？有僵尸，哼，我踩死你。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><img style=\"margin: 10px auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\" alt=\"盘点游戏史上最弱鸡的十大游戏主角\" src=\"http://p9.pstatp.com/large/3e5f0001fbe08c9c2c88\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); text-transform: none; line-height: 16px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"></p><h1 style=\"margin: 36px 0px 22px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; line-height: 32px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 24px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 700; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">No.1 《模拟人生》</h1><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">喂喂，模拟人生本来就是以普通人为主角的游戏吧，难不成你还要里面的小人儿飞鸽天打打外星人什么的？</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">话是这么说，但是弱就是弱呀，甚至被鬼吓一下就晕过去了。入选本榜单毫无压力啊。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><img style=\"margin: 10px auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\" alt=\"盘点游戏史上最弱鸡的十大游戏主角\" src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/3e630001f48535cce37d\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); text-transform: none; line-height: 16px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"></p><hr style=\"background: rgb(237, 64, 64); margin: 40px auto; padding: 0px; border: currentColor; border-image: none; width: 64px; height: 4px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; overflow: visible; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: content-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"/><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">想要收到更多的游戏推荐、想要了解更多的游戏历史，点击右上角的关注哦！</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">分享游戏咨询，推荐游戏评测，</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">普及游戏知识，体验游戏人生。</p>', null);
INSERT INTO `art_content` VALUES ('53196252', '<p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">RNG上单Letme今天几次排到小狗对面，排位还吃了小狗三分，这次又排到小狗对面，Uzi怒了：这次你能赢我把头给你，然后Letme看了下自己方的阵容对Uzi说：这局SKT下路双排。Uzi看了一下自己队友到底是谁，看到厂长，一秒懵了：我们是....clearlove辅助？他真的要辅助，他居然不要位置。于是就有了这样的对话：</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><img style=\"margin: 10px auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\" alt=\"Uzi打赌这局一定赢，结果看到己方辅助是厂长，顿时愣了一秒\" src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/40240003108da50b37cc\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">厂长一脸淡定：我辅助很强！！！于是就有了LPL的牌面，王牌ADC uzi和王牌 打野，不，是辅助 厂长</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><img style=\"margin: 10px auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\" alt=\"Uzi打赌这局一定赢，结果看到己方辅助是厂长，顿时愣了一秒\" src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/40240003108cfbf7a2f4\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">最后一波团战，Uzi不该上的，其实是大顺风，16-5-10实力Carry，但是世界上没有后悔药吃，如果自己不上我方就损失一个人，但是上了，就是团战输了，输了就是被人一波推家，Uzi十分懊恼：我真不该上，应该卖，这把我这么Carry，肯定能赢的。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><img style=\"margin: 10px auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\" alt=\"Uzi打赌这局一定赢，结果看到己方辅助是厂长，顿时愣了一秒\" src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/40240003108b6d6bc3cc\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">Uzi直播五连跪，Uzi：我真的是Carry啊，没把都是Carry，但是没办法，队友乱搞</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><img style=\"margin: 10px auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\" alt=\"Uzi打赌这局一定赢，结果看到己方辅助是厂长，顿时愣了一秒\" src=\"http://p1.pstatp.com/large/40260002f90ecf1dcf54\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">厂长的璐璐，也是跟在Uzi旁边打出2-7-19的战绩，可怜我狗的分</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><img style=\"margin: 10px auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\" alt=\"Uzi打赌这局一定赢，结果看到己方辅助是厂长，顿时愣了一秒\" src=\"http://p9.pstatp.com/large/40240003108962e6d218\"/></p>', null);
INSERT INTO `art_content` VALUES ('53196253', '<p><span style=\"font-size:24px\">&nbsp; &nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">有人问我柠檬网编写的新闻怎么上推荐，现在我告诉你，微信转我50块，我在数据库帮你调到推荐。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8080/ningmengtoutiao/op-plugin/umeditor1.2.3-utf8-jsp/jsp/newsImgUpload/20171205/68121512469265380.jpg\"/></span></p>', null);
INSERT INTO `art_content` VALUES ('53196254', '<p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8080/ningmengtoutiao/op-plugin/umeditor1.2.3-utf8-jsp/jsp/newsImgUpload/20171205/80281512477337491.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">今日，抽象工作室的陈经理重新拿起了自拍杆，再次开启了自己的直播旅程。不过，大家可以很明显的看到，他不是在工作室直播，而是到了一个见不得人的地</span><span style=\"font-size: large;\">方。。。</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8080/ningmengtoutiao/op-plugin/umeditor1.2.3-utf8-jsp/jsp/newsImgUpload/20171205/27041512477543608.jpg\"/></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 从直播内容上看，大家都能猜出他的新“职业”了，生活的重担终究还是压垮了这个男人最后的一点尊严，这是大家都不愿意看到的。又是一年冬季，华尔街的雪又飘起来了，可今年却又感觉特别冷。</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 随着抽象工作室的倒闭，每个直播员都面临着以后“出路”的问题。以前的陈经理在那群臭鱼烂虾直播员面前，总能表现出一丝儒雅不俗的气质，大家都觉得，有文化的读书人就应该是这样的吧。相信现在的陈经理只是暂时的迷茫，从以前的直播平台大明星，到现在的无业游民，他只是有些许不适应罢了。</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 人生这条路太漫长，我们容许自己有暂时的颓废堕落，但一定要相信辉煌时刻谁都会有，拍拍灰尘咱们继续走。</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8080/ningmengtoutiao/op-plugin/umeditor1.2.3-utf8-jsp/jsp/newsImgUpload/20171205/59611512479768979.jpg\"/></span></p>', null);
